          "",
          "können  = can      müssen  = must",
          "dürfen  = may      wollen  = want to",
          "sollen  = should   möchten = would like",
          "",
          "STRUCTURE: Modal + infinitive at the END",
          "",
          "Ich kann Deutsch sprechen.",
          "(I can speak German)",
          "",
          "Du musst heute arbeiten.",
          "(You must work today)",
          "",
          "Notice: The main verb (sprechen, arbeiten)",
          "stays in infinitive form and goes to the end!"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion zwei"
      }
    ]
