        "content": [
          "Every German noun has a GENDER:",
          "",
          "der = MASCULINE    (der Mann, der Tisch)",
          "die = FEMININE     (die Frau, die Minute)",
          "das = NEUTER       (das Kind, das Haus)",
          "",
          "PLURAL = die",
          "",
          "WARNING: Gender is often random!",
          "The word for \"girl\" (das Mädchen) is neuter!",
          "",
          "STRATEGY: Always learn the ARTICLE with",
          "the noun. Never learn \"Minute\" - learn",
          "\"die Minute\". Say it together every time!",
          "",
          "You'll see patterns emerge, but for now:",
          "memorize each article as part of the word."
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion vier"
      }
    ]
