        "content": [
          "German has TWO ways to say \"no/not\":",
          "",
          "nicht = not (negates verbs & adjectives)",
          "kein  = no/not a (negates nouns)",
          "",
          "NICHT - Position varies:",
          "Ich verstehe nicht. (I don't understand)",
          "Das ist nicht gut. (That's not good)",
          "",
          "KEIN - Replaces the article:",
          "",
          "Ich habe einen Hund.",
          "→ Ich habe keinen Hund.",
          "(I have a dog → I don't have a dog)",
          "",
          "RULE: Use kein with NOUNS,",
          "      Use nicht with everything else!"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion sieben"
      }
    ]
